-VOCALIST: Hey!

24:30.686 --> 24:31.470
Another.

24:33.602 --> 24:35.474
-Ooh, ooh, ooh.

24:37.345 --> 24:38.738
-Text me.
-Nope.

24:46.833 --> 24:48.225
-Mom.
-Yes?

24:48.269 --> 24:50.793
-Okay. I want
a big party this year.
-Serious?

24:50.837 --> 24:52.795
-I want a quinceañera.
-Quinceañera?

24:52.839 --> 24:56.277
We can't do that.
We're too white for that.
We're not allowed.

25:05.852 --> 25:08.811
Do me a favor?Never look me in the eye again.

25:08.855 --> 25:11.814
Okay? 'Cause your stare
is way too intense.

25:11.858 --> 25:13.599
It's starting to make
my hair fall out.

25:19.082 --> 25:20.997
Our women do not
consider themselves

25:21.041 --> 25:22.608
enslaved by marriage.

25:25.393 --> 25:30.703
And they certainly
do not want to sacrifice
their present privileges

25:30.746 --> 25:33.488
for some phony equality
with men.

